      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ENOLA (2) returns from a spell of four months. Last raced when she scored by 25 metres at Bendigo and was midfield at Group 1 level prior. Readied with a trial win and should have no excuses from this advantageous draw. Expecting a bright start to the campaign. CLASSIC CHIP (6) finished eighth in the Group 1 Breeders Challenge final when last seen here in October but came from this barrier to win a semi final of that series prior. Readied with two trials and looms as a significant threat. DEVIOUS MINDS (1) comes through the Gold Bracelet series at Bathurst where she was runner-up in the heats. Can feature from an ideal draw. SENTOSAR (8) draws wide but may have the hoof on the till after a last-start second in a Gold Chalice consolation.",
